✅ ADX Indicator ရဲ့ အဓိပ္ပါယ်
ADX Value	Market Condition
0 - 20	Weak Trend (or ranging)
20 - 25	Emerging Trend (watching)
25 - 50	Strong Trend
50 - 75	Very Strong Trend
75 - 100	Extremely Strong Trend

👉 ADX က “trend direction” မပြဘူး၊ “trend strength” ပဲပြတယ်။

🧠 ADX Structure (3 lines)
+DI (Positive Directional Indicator) – Buyers control

−DI (Negative Directional Indicator) – Sellers control

ADX – The average difference between +DI and -DI over time

ADX ကို မိမိရွေးချယ်တဲ့ period (ဥပမာ 14) ပေါ်မူတည်ပြီး +DI နဲ့ −DI တွေရဲ့ divergence ကို smooth average လုပ်တာဖြစ်တယ်။

🧮 Calculation Summary
True Range (TR) = max(high - low, abs(high - prev close), abs(low - prev close))

+DM / -DM (Directional Movement) = directional price change

Smooth these values over n-period (default 14)

Calculate +DI / -DI

diff
Copy
Edit
+DI = 100 * (Smoothed +DM / ATR)
-DI = 100 * (Smoothed -DM / ATR)
DX = 100 * |(+DI - -DI)| / (+DI + -DI)

ADX = EMA of DX over time (default 14)

📈 Signal Usage
✅ Trending Market Confirmation
ADX > 25 → trending market

ADX rising → trend getting stronger

ADX falling → trend weakening (may enter consolidation)

✅ Combine with DI
+DI > -DI and ADX rising → strong uptrend

-DI > +DI and ADX rising → strong downtrend

ADX falling → avoid trend-following strategies

✅ Strategy Use Case
text
Copy
Edit
IF (ADX > 25 AND +DI > -DI) THEN
   BUY signal (strong uptrend)
ELSE IF (ADX > 25 AND -DI > +DI) THEN
   SELL signal (strong downtrend)
ELSE
   SIDEWAYS → skip or range strategy


   ✅ အသုံးဝင်တဲ့အချက်များ
   ADX > 25 ဆိုရင် trending market ဖြစ်တယ်။

   +DI > -DI ဆိုရင် Uptrend

   -DI > +DI ဆိုရင် Downtrend

